name: Solutions Archive
tagline: My solutions for ICPC-like problems from various online judges
body:
### Welcome to my Solutions Archive.
I started collecting my accepted solutions for ICPC-like problems from 2012.  
In December 2015 I started transferring my solutions to GitHub. _(and it still continues)_  
I will keep solving new problems and I will update this repository with my accepted solutions.  


### Solutions
Visit the [repository](https://github.com/KayvanMazaheri/acm) for solutions.  
There are solutions for many problems from various online judges:  
+ [ACM-ICPC Live Archive](http://livearchive.onlinejudge.org)
+ [Uva Online Judge](http://uva.onlinejudge.org)
+ [Saratov State University :: Online Contester](http://acm.sgu.ru)
+ [USA Computing Olympiad](http://www.usaco.org) (online contests)
+ [USACO Training Gateway](http://train.usaco.org/usacogate)
+ [Project Euler](https://projecteuler.net)

### About Me
Visit my GitHub page [here](http://KayvanMazaheri.github.io)
